noria:CR_WebSrvUpgrade_20240501 noria:changeRequestSpecification <kos/ChangeRequest/specification/OSUpgradeProcedure> ;
    noria:changeRequestImpact noria:OP_WebSrvUpgradeProcedure . # Linking CR to the specific operation plan

